   <abstract xlink:href="http://lib.lsu.edu/services/oralhistory/abstracts/gillis/Merchant_JW.pdf">Merchant discusses civil rights and its influence on Louisiana politics, he and his
            father's support of civil rights, Gillis Long's gubernatorial and Congressional
            campaigns, Long's relationship with several Louisiana politicians, redistricting of the
            8th U.S. Congressional District of Louisiana, political infighting in the Long family,
            Gillis Long's political positions, his health, and his service to his
            constituents.</abstract>
